00:27:59,427 --> 00:28:01,513
Patrol 18, Patrol 18 on the case.

378
00:28:02,055 --> 00:28:03,473
Who called it in, Officer Song?

379
00:28:03,556 --> 00:28:06,101
<i>The report was made by
